Package: rmdTemplates
Type: Package
Title: A collection of Rmarkdown templates
Version: 0.8.0
Author: F. Rodríguez-Sánchez <f.rodriguez.sanc@gmail.com>. 
Maintainer: F. Rodríguez-Sánchez <f.rodriguez.sanc@gmail.com>
Description: A collection of Rmarkdown templates for 
    writing scientific manuscripts, manuscript reviews, Beamer slides (metropolis theme) 
    and other Rmarkdown documents, with support for cross-references, 
    citations and different bibliography styles. 
License: CC0
URL: https://github.com/Pakillo/rmdTemplates
BugReports: https://github.com/Pakillo/rmdTemplates/issues
Imports:
    base64enc,
    binb,
    knitr,
    knitcitations,
    rmarkdown
Suggests:
    devtools
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
